data.description: Step into this delightful 3-bedroom home nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac. It's been thoughtfully upgraded with fresh paint both inside and out, new flooring, and a modernized kitchen. In addition to a single-car garage, there are two sheds in the backyard, providing ample storage space for your needs. Step onto the spacious back deck, perfect for relaxing and entertaining.
